Subject: Encrypted data on CDROMs  (Was: Pawn shops etc, and a NEW question)
Message-ID: <1992Feb21.214507.855@fzi.de>
Date: 21 Feb 92 21:45:07 GMT
Article-I.D.: fzi.1992Feb21.214507.855
References: <299ffefa.knapper@knapper.cactus.org> <1992Feb21.051907.13198@visix.com>
